### Day-Night Cycle

A slow global transition affecting all elements.

```scheme
(define (daylight t)
  (* 0.5 (+ 1 (sin (* t 0.8)))))

(define (scene t)
  (let ((d (daylight t)))
    (world
      ;; sky
      (entity 'rect
        (position 0 0)
        (size 400 300)
        (color (* 100 d) (* 150 d) (* 200 d)))
      ;; sun/moon
      (entity 'circle
        (position 200 (+ 80 (* 60 (- 1 d))))
        (radius 20)
        (color (* 255 d) (* 230 d) (* 180 d)))
      ;; ground
      (entity 'rect
        (position 0 300)
        (size 400 100)
        (color (* 80 d) (* 100 d) (* 60 d))))))

(motion scene 0 10 1/30)
```

