### Chain Reaction

One event triggering the next in sequence.

```scheme
(define (trigger i delay t)
  (max 0 (- t (* i delay))))

(define (pop i delay t)
  (let ((local (trigger i delay t)))
    (if (< local 0.5)
        (* 30 (- 0.5 local))
        0)))

(define (scene t)
  (world
    (entity 'circle
      (position 100 200)
      (radius (+ 10 (pop 0 0.5 t)))
      (color 200 100 100))
    (entity 'circle
      (position 200 200)
      (radius (+ 10 (pop 1 0.5 t)))
      (color 100 200 100))
    (entity 'circle
      (position 300 200)
      (radius (+ 10 (pop 2 0.5 t)))
      (color 100 100 200))))

(motion scene 0 4 1/30)
```

[VISUAL: Three circles, red, green, blue, each briefly inflating in sequence from left to right.]

A domino fall.

