### The Looping Narrative

A figure entering, crossing, and exiting, then repeating.

```scheme
(define (actor-x t)
  (let ((local (modulo t 6)))
    (cond
      ((< local 1) (+ -20 (* local 50)))        ; enter
      ((< local 4) (+ 30 (* (- local 1) 100)))  ; cross
      ((< local 6) (+ 330 (* (- local 4) 50)))  ; exit
      (else 420))))

(define (scene t)
  (world
    (entity 'circle
      (position (actor-x t) 200)
      (radius 12)
      (color 200 150 100))))

(motion scene 0 12 1/30)
```

