### The Glitching Sign

A stable image interrupted by brief distortions.

```scheme
(define (glitch t)
  (if (and (> (modulo t 3) 2.8) (< (modulo t 3) 2.9))
      (modulo (* t 137) 40)
      0))

(define (scene t)
  (world
    (entity 'rect
      (position (+ 150 (glitch t)) 180)
      (size 100 40)
      (color 200 50 50))
    (entity 'rect
      (position 160 190)
      (size 80 20)
      (color 255 255 255))))

(motion scene 0 9 1/30)
```

[VISUAL: A red rectangle with a white bar (sign); every ~3 seconds, the red bar jumps briefly to the side.]

Digital artifact.

