### The Fading Trail

A moving object leaving a trail that decays over time.

*[needs: particle history / trail rendering]*  
<!-- BUILD: trail effect requires either (a) entity persistence with age-based alpha, or (b) dedicated trail primitive -->

```scheme
(define (leader-x t)
  (+ 100 (* t 40)))

(define (leader-y t)
  (+ 200 (* 30 (sin (* t 3)))))

(define (scene t)
  (world
    ;; leader
    (entity 'circle
      (position (leader-x t) (leader-y t))
      (radius 8)
      (color 200 100 100))
    ;; trail samples (manual history)
    (entity 'circle
      (position (leader-x (- t 0.2)) (leader-y (- t 0.2)))
      (radius 6)
      (color 150 80 80))
    (entity 'circle
      (position (leader-x (- t 0.4)) (leader-y (- t 0.4)))
      (radius 4)
      (color 100 60 60))))

(motion scene 0 6 1/30)
```

[VISUAL: A bright red circle moving; two dimmer, smaller circles trailing behind at fixed time offsets.]

Motion history made visible.

