### The Alarm

A flashing indicator that accelerates as time approaches a threshold.

```scheme
(define (alarm-flash t threshold)
  (let ((remaining (- threshold t)))
    (if (< remaining 0)
        255
        (if (< (modulo t (/ remaining 4)) 0.1)
            255
            100))))

(define (scene t)
  (world
    (entity 'circle
      (position 200 200)
      (radius 30)
      (color (alarm-flash t 5) 100 100))))

(motion scene 0 6 1/30)
```

[VISUAL: A circle that starts dim red, flashing slowly, then faster, then solid bright red after 5 seconds.]

Urgency encoded as frequency.

